msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat tantangan, kunjungi :menuselection:`Pengaturan --> Alat-Alat "
"Gamifikasi --> Tantangan`. Klik :guilabel:`Baru` di pojok atas-kiri untuk "
"membuka formulir tantangan kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:92
msgid "At the top of the form, enter a :guilabel:`Challenge Name`."
msgstr "Di atas formulir, masukkan :guilabel:`Nama Tantangan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:95
