#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:186
msgid "Product variants"
msgstr "Varian-varian produk"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/gelato.rst:138
msgid ""
"To view and edit the newly synchronized product variants, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Attributes & Variants` tab, which will have the variants "
"pulled from the Gelato product configuration. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Configure` button to edit and configure the variant images, "
"delivery methods, additional pricing, etc."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat dan mengedit varian produk yang baru disinkronkan, navigasikan "
"ke tab :guilabel:`Atribut & Varian`, yang akan memiliki varian yang ditarik "
"dari konfigurasi produk Gelato. Klik tombol :guilabel:`Konfigurasi` untuk "
"mengedit dan mengonfigurasi gambar varian, metode pengiriman, harga "
"tambahan, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/gelato.rst:144
msgid "Order a Gelato product from Odoo"
msgstr "Memesan produk Gelato dari Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/gelato.rst:146
msgid ""
"Once synchronized, Gelato products are available to order in Odoo "
"through :doc:`sales quotations <sales_quotations>` or on the **eCommerce** "
"store. Gelato delivery options are automatically synchronized upon API and "
"webhook configuration."
msgstr ""
"Setelah disinkronkan, produk Gelato tersedia untuk dipesan di Odoo melalui "
":doc:`quotation penjualan <sales_quotations>` atau di toko **eCommerce**. "
"Opsi pengiriman Gelato secara otomatis disinkronkan setelah konfigurasi API "
"dan webhook."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/gelato.rst:150
msgid ""
"To add Gelato delivery, click :guilabel:`Add shipping` on the sales order. "
"Select :guilabel:`Standard Delivery` or :guilabel:`Express Delivery` in "
"the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` field, then click :guilabel:`Get rate`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan pengiriman Gelato, klik :guilabel:`Tambah pengiriman` pada "
"Sales Order. Pilih :guilabel:`Standard Delivery` atau :guilabel:`Express "
"Delivery` pada field :guilabel:`Metode Pengiriman`, kemudian klik "
":guilabel:`Dapatkan tarif`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/gelato.rst:154
msgid ""
"Once the quotation is confirmed, it becomes an active sales order, and the "
"order is sent to Gelato for fulfillment. Once a sales order is sent from "
"Odoo to Gelato, Gelato processes the order, produces the product at the "
"nearest fulfillment center, and ships it directly to the end-customer."
msgstr ""
"Setelah quotation dikonfirmasi, quotation menjadi Sales Order aktif, dan "
"pesanan dikirim ke Gelato untuk dipenuhi. Setelah Sales Order dikirim dari "
"Odoo ke Gelato, Gelato memproses pesanan, memproduksi produk di pusat "
"pemenuhan terdekat, dan mengirimkannya langsung ke pelanggan akhir."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/gelato.rst:159
msgid ":doc:`sales_quotations/create_quotations`"
msgstr ":doc:`sales_quotations/create_quotations`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/gelato.rst:162
msgid ""
"When creating a sales order for Gelato products in the database, only Gelato "
"products can be added to the same sales order. Multivendor orders are not "
"available with the Gelato connector at this time."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat Sales Order untuk produk Gelato di database, hanya produk "
"Gelato yang dapat ditambahkan ke Sales Order yang sama. Pesanan multivendor "
"tidak tersedia dengan konektor Gelato saat ini."

