"pengiriman sebelum mengirim faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:57
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab of the :guilabel:`Customer Invoice "
"Draft`, the down payment that was configured in the *Create invoice(s)* pop-"
"up form appears under a new :guilabel:`Down Payments` section."
