"Generated eWallets can be accessed through the :guilabel:`eWallets` smart "
"button in the upper-right corner. From there, :guilabel:`Send` "
"or :guilabel:`Share` the eWallets via email or a URL link."
msgstr ""
"eWallet yang dihasilkan dapat diakses melalui tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`eWallet` di sudut kanan atas. Dari sana, :guilabel:`Kirim` atau "
":guilabel:`Bagikan` eWallet melalui email atau tautan URL."

