"Sebuah perusahaan pakaian memiliki rincian varian berikut untuk salah satu "
"kaos terlaris mereka:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:15
msgid "Unisex Classic Tee"
msgstr "Kaos Klasik Unisex"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:17
msgid "Color: Blue, Red, White, Black"
msgstr "Warna: Biru, Merah, Putih, Hitam"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:18
msgid "Size: S, M, L, XL, XXL"
msgstr "Ukuran: S, M, L, XL, XXL"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:20
msgid ""
"Here, the **T-shirt** is the product template, and **T-shirt: Blue, S** is a "
"specific product variant."
msgstr ""
"Di sini, **Kaos** adalah templat produk, dan **Kaos: Biru, S** adalah varian "
"produk spesifik."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Color** and **Size** are *attributes*, and the corresponding options (like "
"**Blue** and **S**) are *values*."
msgstr ""
"**Warna** dan **Ukuran** adalah *atribut*, dan opsi yang sesuai (seperti "
"**Biru** dan **S**) adalah *nilai*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:26
msgid ""
"In this instance, there is a total of twenty different product variants: "
"four **Color** options multiplied by five **Size** options. Each variant has "
"its own inventory count, sales totals, and other similar records in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Dalam hal ini, terdapat total dua puluh varian produk yang berbeda: empat "
"opsi **Warna** dikalikan dengan lima opsi **Ukuran**. Setiap varian memiliki "
"jumlah inventaris, total penjualan, dan catatan serupa lainnya sendiri di "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:31
msgid ":ref:`ecommerce/products/product-variants`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:36
msgid ""
"To use product variants, the *Variants* setting **must** be activated in the "
"Odoo *Sales* application."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:39
msgid ""
"To do that, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"and locate the :guilabel:`Product Catalog` section at the top of the page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:42
msgid ""
"In that section, check the box to enable the :guilabel:`Variants` feature."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"Activating product variants on the Settings page of the Odoo Sales "
"application."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:47
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Save` at the top of the :guilabel:`Settings` page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:50
msgid "Attributes"
msgstr "Atribut"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:52
msgid ""
"Before product variants can be set up, attributes **must** be created. To "
"create, manage, and modify attributes, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Configuration --> Attributes`."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum varian produk dapat diatur, atribut **harus** dibuat terlebih "
"dahulu. Untuk membuat, mengelola, dan mengubah atribut, buka "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Penjualan --> Konfigurasi --> Atribut`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:56
msgid ""
"The order of attributes on the :guilabel:`Attributes` page dictates how they "
"appear on the *Product Configurator*, *Point of Sale* dashboard, and "
"*eCommerce* pages."
msgstr ""
"Urutan atribut pada halaman :guilabel:`Attributes` menentukan bagaimana "
"atribut tersebut muncul pada *Product Configurator*, dashboard *POS*, dan "
"halaman *eCommerce*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:59
msgid ""
"To create a new attribute from the :guilabel:`Attributes` page, "
"click :guilabel:`New`. Doing so reveals a blank attributes form that can be "
"customized and configured in a number of ways."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat atribut baru dari halaman :guilabel:`Attributes`, klik "
":guilabel:`New`. Tindakan ini akan menampilkan formulir atribut kosong yang "
"dapat disesuaikan dan dikonfigurasi dengan berbagai cara."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid "A blank attribute creation form in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr "Formulir pembuatan atribut kosong di aplikasi Penjualan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:65
msgid "First, create an :guilabel:`Attribute Name`, such as `Color` or `Size`."
msgstr "Pertama, buat :guilabel:`Attribute Name`, seperti `Color` atau `Size`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:67
msgid ""
"Next, select one of the options from the :guilabel:`Display Type` field. "
"The :guilabel:`Display Type` determines how this product is shown on the "
"online store, *Point of Sale* dashboard, and *Product Configurator*."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, pilih salah satu opsi dari kolom :guilabel:`Display Type`. "
":guilabel:`Display Type` menentukan bagaimana produk ini ditampilkan di toko "
"online, dashboard *POS*, dan *Product Configurator*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:71
msgid "The :guilabel:`Display Type` options are:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:73
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pills`: options appear as selectable buttons on the product page "
"of the online store."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:74
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Color`: options appear as small, colored squares, which reflect "
"any HTML color codes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:75
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Radio`: options appear in a bullet-style list on the product page "
"of the online store."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Select`: options appear in a drop-down menu on the product page "
"of the online store. set, on the product page of the online store."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Multi-checkbox`: options appear as selectable checkboxes on the "
"product page of the online store."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid "Display Types on Product Configurator on the online store in Odoo."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:84
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Variant Creation Mode` field informs Odoo when to "
"automatically create a new variant once an attribute is added to a product."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:88
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Variant Creation Mode` field **must** be set "
"to :guilabel:`Never` in order for the :guilabel:`Multi-checkbox` to work "
"properly as the :guilabel:`Display Type`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Instantly`: Creates all possible variants as soon as attributes "
"and values are added to a product template."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Instantly`: Membuat semua kemungkinan varian segera setelah "
"atribut dan nilai ditambahkan ke templat produk."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dynamically`: Creates variants **only** when corresponding "
"attributes and values are added to a sales order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dynamically`: Membuat varian **hanya** ketika atribut dan nilai "
"yang sesuai ditambahkan ke sales order."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Never`: Prevents the automatic creation of purchaseable variants "
"with this tag. Instead, this tag is treated as being informational. If more "
"than one value is assigned to an attribute with this tag, all values are "
"loaded when the product displays, since the creation of discrete variants is "
"prevented."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Never`: Mencegah pembuatan otomatis varian yang dapat dibeli "
"dengan tag ini. Sebaliknya, tag ini dianggap sebagai informasional. Jika "
"lebih dari satu nilai diberikan ke atribut dengan tag ini, semua nilai "
"dimuat ketika produk ditampilkan, karena pembuatan varian diskrit dicegah."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:101
msgid ""
"Once added to a product, an attribute's :guilabel:`Variants Creation Mode` "
"cannot be edited."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:103
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`eCommerce Filter Visibility` field determines whether or not "
"these attribute options are visible to the customer on the front-end, as "
"they shop on the online store."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`eCommerce Filter Visibility` menentukan apakah opsi "
"atribut ini terlihat oleh pelanggan di front-end saat mereka berbelanja di "
"toko online."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Visible`: the attribute values are visible to customers on the "
"front-end."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Visible`: nilai atribut terlihat oleh pelanggan di front-end."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:107
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Hidden`: the attribute values are hidden from customers on the "
"front-end."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hidden`: nilai atribut disembunyikan dari pelanggan di front-end."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:109
msgid ""
"Lastly, in the optional :guilabel:`eCommerce Category` field, select a "
"category from a drop-down menu to group similar attributes under the same "
"section for added specificity and organization."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, dalam bidang opsional :guilabel:`eCommerce Category`, pilih "
"kategori dari menu drop-down untuk mengelompokkan atribut serupa di bawah "
"bagian yang sama untuk spesifisitas dan organisasi tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:113
msgid ""
"To view the details related to the attribute category selected, click the "
"internal link :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(right arrow)` icon to the "
"far-right of the :guilabel:`eCommerce Category` field, once an option has "
"been selected. Doing so reveals that attribute category's detail form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat detail terkait kategori atribut yang dipilih, klik ikon tautan "
"internal :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(right arrow)` di sisi kanan "
"bidang :guilabel:`eCommerce Category` setelah opsi dipilih. Melakukan ini "
"akan menampilkan formulir detail kategori atribut tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"A standard attribute category detail page accessible via its internal link "
"arrow icon."
msgstr ""
"Halaman detail kategori atribut standar yang dapat diakses melalui ikon "
"panah tautan internalnya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:121
msgid ""
"Here, the :guilabel:`Category Name` and :guilabel:`Sequence` are displayed "
"at the top. Followed by :guilabel:`Related Attributes` associated with the "
"category. These attributes can be dragged and dropped into a desired "
"priority order."
msgstr ""
"Di sini, :guilabel:`Category Name` dan :guilabel:`Sequence` ditampilkan di "
"bagian atas. Diikuti oleh :guilabel:`Related Attributes` yang terkait dengan "
"kategori. Atribut ini dapat diseret dan dijatuhkan ke dalam urutan prioritas "
"yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:125
msgid ""
"Attributes can be directly added to the category, as well, by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr ""
"Atribut juga dapat langsung ditambahkan ke kategori dengan mengklik "
":guilabel:`Add a line`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:128
msgid ""
"To create an attribute category directly from this field, start typing the "
"name of the new category, then select either :guilabel:`Create` "
"or :guilabel:`Create and edit...` from the drop-down menu that appears."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat kategori atribut langsung dari bidang ini, mulai ketik nama "
"kategori baru, lalu pilih :guilabel:`Create` atau :guilabel:`Create and "
"edit...` dari menu drop-down yang muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:132
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Create` creates the category, which can be modified "
"later. Clicking :guilabel:`Create and edit...` creates the category and "
"reveals a :guilabel:`Create Category` pop-up window, in which the new "
"attribute category can be configured and customized."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik :guilabel:`Create` membuat kategori yang dapat dimodifikasi nanti. "
"Mengklik :guilabel:`Create and edit...` membuat kategori dan menampilkan "
"jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Create Category`, di mana kategori atribut baru "
"dapat dikonfigurasi dan disesuaikan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:137
msgid "Attribute values"
msgstr "Nilai atribut"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:139
msgid ""
"Attribute values should be added to the :guilabel:`Attribute Values` tab. "
"Values can be added to an attribute at any time, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Nilai atribut harus ditambahkan ke tab :guilabel:`Attribute Values`. Nilai "
"dapat ditambahkan ke atribut kapan saja jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:142
msgid ""
"To add a value, click :guilabel:`Add a line` in the :guilabel:`Attribute "
"Values` tab."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan nilai, klik :guilabel:`Add a line` di tab "
":guilabel:`Attribute Values`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:144
msgid ""
"Then, enter the name of the value in the :guilabel:`Value` column. Next, "
"check the box in the :guilabel:`Is custom value` column if the value is "
"custom (i.e., the customer gets to provide unique specifications that are "
"specific to this particular value)."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, masukkan nama nilai di kolom :guilabel:`Value`. Selanjutnya, "
"centang kotak di kolom :guilabel:`Is custom value` jika nilai bersifat "
"kustom (yaitu, pelanggan dapat memberikan spesifikasi unik yang khusus untuk "
"nilai tertentu ini)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:149
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Warna"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:151
msgid ""
"Next to :guilabel:`Display Type`, select the :guilabel:`Color` option. Go to "
"the :guilabel:`Attribute Values` tab to modify the value settings."
msgstr ""
"Di samping :guilabel:`Display Type`, pilih opsi :guilabel:`Color`. Buka tab "
":guilabel:`Attribute Values` untuk mengubah pengaturan nilai."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid "Add an image of the pattern to an attribute."
msgstr "Tambahkan gambar pola ke atribut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:157
msgid ""
"To choose a color, click the blank circle in the :guilabel:`Color` column, "
"which reveals an HTML color selector pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih warna, klik lingkaran kosong di kolom :guilabel:`Color`, yang "
"akan menampilkan jendela pop-up pemilih warna HTML."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"Selecting a color from the HTML color pop-up window that appears on "
"attribute form."
msgstr ""
"Memilih warna dari jendela pop-up warna HTML yang muncul pada formulir "
"atribut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:163
msgid ""
"In this pop-up window, select a specific color by dragging the color slider "
"to a particular hue and clicking on the color portion directly on the color "
"gradient window."
msgstr ""
"Dalam jendela pop-up ini, pilih warna tertentu dengan menyeret penggeser "
"warna ke nuansa tertentu dan mengklik langsung pada bagian warna di jendela "
"gradien warna."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:166
msgid ""
"Or, choose a specific color by clicking the *dropper* icon and selecting a "
"desired color that's currently clickable on the screen."
msgstr ""
"Atau, pilih warna tertentu dengan mengklik ikon *pipet* dan pilih warna yang "
"diinginkan yang saat ini dapat diklik di layar."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:169
msgid ""
"If you sell products with specific patterns, you can also add an image to "
"display the pattern of the product. To do so, click the :icon:`fa-"
"camera` :guilabel:`(camera)` icon, then click the :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon and select an image from your local drive. "
"This pattern will appear as a color option on the eCommerce product page."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda menjual produk dengan pola tertentu, Anda juga dapat menambahkan "
"gambar untuk menampilkan pola produk tersebut. Untuk melakukannya, klik ikon "
":icon:`fa-camera` :guilabel:`(kamera)`, lalu klik ikon :icon:`fa-pencil` "
":guilabel:`(pensil)` dan pilih gambar dari drive lokal Anda. Pola ini akan "
"muncul sebagai opsi warna di halaman produk eCommerce."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid "Pattern as color option on the eCommerce page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:178
msgid ""
"Attributes can also be created directly from the product template by adding "
"a new line and typing the name into the :guilabel:`Variants` tab."
msgstr ""
"Atribut juga dapat dibuat langsung dari templat produk dengan menambahkan "
"baris baru dan mengetikkan nama ke tab :guilabel:`Variants`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:181
msgid ""
"Once an attribute is added to a product, that product is listed and "
"accessible via the attribute's :guilabel:`Related Products` smart button. "
"That button lists every product in the database currently using that "
"attribute."
msgstr ""
"Setelah atribut ditambahkan ke produk, produk tersebut terdaftar dan dapat "
"diakses melalui tombol pintar :guilabel:`Produk Terkait` atribut. Tombol "
"tersebut mencantumkan setiap produk dalam database yang saat ini menggunakan "
"atribut tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:188
msgid ""
"Once an attribute is created, use the attribute (and its values) to create a "
"product variant. To do that, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --"
"> Products`, and select an existing product to view that desired product's "
"form. Or, click :guilabel:`Create` to create a new product, to which a "
"product variant can be added."
msgstr ""
"Setelah atribut dibuat, gunakan atribut (dan nilainya) untuk membuat varian "
"produk. Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Products`, dan pilih produk yang ada untuk melihat formulir produk yang "
"diinginkan. Atau, klik :guilabel:`Create` untuk membuat produk baru, yang "
"dapat ditambahkan varian produknya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:193
msgid ""
"On the product form, click the :guilabel:`Attributes \\& Variants` tab to "
"view, manage, and modify attributes and values for the product."
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir produk, klik tab :guilabel:`Attributes \\& Variants` untuk "
"melihat, mengelola, dan mengubah atribut dan nilai untuk produk."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid "The attributes and values tab on a typical product form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Tab atribut dan nilai pada formulir produk tipikal di Penjualan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:199
msgid ""
"To add an attribute to a product and subsequent attribute values, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a line` in the :guilabel:`Attributes \\& Variants` tab. "
"Then, choose the desired attribute from the drop-down menu that appears."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan atribut ke produk dan nilai atribut berikutnya, klik "
":guilabel:`Tambahkan baris` di tab :guilabel:`Atribut \\& Varian`. Kemudian, "
"pilih atribut yang diinginkan dari menu drop-down yang muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:204
msgid ""
"Attributes can be created directly from the :guilabel:`Attributes \\& "
"Variants` tab of a product form. To do that, start typing the name of the "
"new attribute in the blank field, and select either :guilabel:`Create` "
"or :guilabel:`Create and edit...` from the mini drop-down menu that appears."
msgstr ""
"Atribut dapat dibuat langsung dari tab :guilabel:`Attributes \\& Variants` "
"pada formulir produk. Untuk melakukannya, mulai ketik nama atribut baru di "
"kolom kosong, dan pilih :guilabel:`Create` atau :guilabel:`Create and "
"edit...` dari menu drop-down mini yang muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:209
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Create` creates the attribute, which can be customized "
"later. Clicking :guilabel:`Create and edit...` creates the attribute, and "
"a :guilabel:`Create Attribute` pop-up form appears. In the pop-up form, "
"proceed to modify the attribute in a number of ways."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik :guilabel:`Create` akan membuat atribut, yang dapat disesuaikan "
"nanti. Mengklik :guilabel:`Create and edit...` akan membuat atribut, dan "
"formulir pop-up :guilabel:`Create Attribute` akan muncul. Dalam formulir pop-"
"up, lanjutkan untuk mengubah atribut dengan berbagai cara."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:213
msgid ""
"Once an attribute is selected in the :guilabel:`Attribute` column, proceed "
"to select the specific attribute values to apply to the product, via the "
"drop-down menu available in the :guilabel:`Values` column."
msgstr ""
"Setelah atribut dipilih di kolom :guilabel:`Attribute`, lanjutkan untuk "
"memilih nilai atribut spesifik yang akan diterapkan pada produk, melalui "
"menu drop-down yang tersedia di kolom :guilabel:`Values`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:218
msgid "There is no limit to how many values can be added."
msgstr "Tidak ada batasan berapa banyak nilai yang dapat ditambahkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:221
msgid ""
"Similar product variant creation processes are accessible through the "
"Purchase, Inventory, and eCommerce applications."
msgstr ""
"Proses pembuatan varian produk serupa dapat diakses melalui aplikasi "
"Pembelian, Inventaris, dan eCommerce."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:227
msgid "Configure variants"
msgstr "Konfigurasi varian"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:229
msgid ""
"To the far-right of the attribute line is a :guilabel:`Configure` button. "
"When clicked, Odoo reveals a separate page showcasing those "
"specific :guilabel:`Product Variant Values`."
msgstr ""
"Di paling kanan baris atribut terdapat tombol :guilabel:`Configure`. Ketika "
"diklik, Odoo menampilkan halaman terpisah yang menunjukkan "
":guilabel:`Product Variant Values` spesifik tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Product Variant Values page accessible via the Configure button on a "
"product form."
msgstr ""
"Halaman Product Variant Values yang dapat diakses melalui tombol Configure "
"pada formulir produk."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:235
msgid ""
"Here, the specific :guilabel:`Value` name, :guilabel:`HTML Color Index` (if "
"applicable), and :guilabel:`Value Price Extra` are viewable."
msgstr ""
"Di sini, nama :guilabel:`Value` spesifik, :guilabel:`HTML Color Index` (jika "
"berlaku), dan :guilabel:`Value Price Extra` dapat dilihat."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:239
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Value Price Extra` represents the increase in the sales price "
"if the attribute is selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Value Price Extra` menunjukkan kenaikan harga jual jika atribut "
"tersebut dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:242
msgid ""
"When a value is clicked on the :guilabel:`Product Variant Values` page, Odoo "
"reveals a separate page, detailing that value's related details."
msgstr ""
"Ketika suatu nilai diklik pada halaman :guilabel:`Product Variant Values`, "
"Odoo menampilkan halaman terpisah yang merinci detail terkait nilai tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"A Product Variant Values page accessible via the Product Variants Values "
"general page."
msgstr ""
"Halaman Product Variant Values yang dapat diakses melalui halaman umum "
"Product Variants Values."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:248
msgid ""
"On the specific product variant detail page, the :guilabel:`Value` "
"and :guilabel:`Value Price Extra` fields can be found, along with "
"an :guilabel:`Exclude for` field."
msgstr ""
"Pada halaman detail varian produk spesifik, bidang :guilabel:`Value` dan "
":guilabel:`Value Price Extra` dapat ditemukan, beserta bidang "
":guilabel:`Exclude for`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:251
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Exclude for` field, different :guilabel:`Product "
"Templates` and specific :guilabel:`Attribute Values` can be added. When "
"added, this specific attribute value will be excluded from those specific "
"products."
msgstr ""
"Dalam bidang :guilabel:`Exclude for`, :guilabel:`Product Templates` yang "
"berbeda dan :guilabel:`Attribute Values` spesifik dapat ditambahkan. Ketika "
"ditambahkan, nilai atribut spesifik ini akan dikecualikan dari produk-produk "
"spesifik tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:256
msgid "Variants smart button"
msgstr "Tombol pintar Variants"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:258
msgid ""
"When a product has attributes and variants configured in "
"its :guilabel:`Attributes \\& Variants` tab, a :guilabel:`Variants` smart "
"button appears at the top of the product form. The :guilabel:`Variants` "
"smart button indicates how many variants are currently configured for that "
"specific product."
msgstr ""
"Ketika suatu produk memiliki atribut dan varian yang dikonfigurasi dalam tab "
":guilabel:`Attributes \\& Variants`, tombol pintar :guilabel:`Variants` "
"muncul di bagian atas formulir produk. Tombol pintar :guilabel:`Variants` "
"menunjukkan berapa banyak varian yang saat ini dikonfigurasi untuk produk "
"spesifik tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid "The variants smart button at the top of the product form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Tombol pintar variants di bagian atas formulir produk di Odoo Penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:265
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Variants` smart button is clicked, Odoo reveals a "
"separate page showcasing all the specific product variant combinations "
"configured for that specific product."
msgstr ""
"Ketika tombol pintar :guilabel:`Variants` diklik, Odoo menampilkan halaman "
"terpisah yang menunjukkan semua kombinasi varian produk spesifik yang "
"dikonfigurasi untuk produk spesifik tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"The variants page accessible via the variants smart button on the product "
"form in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Halaman variants yang dapat diakses melalui tombol pintar variants pada "
"formulir produk di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:272
msgid "Impact of variants"
msgstr "Dampak varian"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:274
msgid ""
"In addition to offering more detailed product options to customers, product "
"variants have their own impacts that can be taken advantage of throughout "
"the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Selain menawarkan opsi produk yang lebih detail kepada pelanggan, varian "
"produk memiliki dampaknya sendiri yang dapat dimanfaatkan di seluruh "
"database Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:277
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Barcode`: barcodes are associated with each variant, instead of "
"the product template. Each individual variant can have its own unique "
"barcode/SKU."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Barcode`: barcode dikaitkan dengan setiap varian, bukan template "
"produk. Setiap varian individual dapat memiliki barcode/SKU uniknya sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:279
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Price`: every product variant has its own public price, which is "
"the sum of the product template price *and* any extra charges for particular "
"attributes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Price`: setiap varian produk memiliki harga publiknya sendiri, "
"yang merupakan jumlah dari harga template produk *dan* biaya tambahan untuk "
"atribut tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:283
msgid ""
"A red shirt's sales price is $23 -- because the shirt's template price is "
"$20, plus an additional $3 for the red color variant. Pricelist rules can be "
"configured to apply to the product template or to the variant."
msgstr ""
"Harga jual kemeja merah adalah $23 -- karena harga template kemeja adalah "
"$20, ditambah $3 tambahan untuk varian warna merah. Aturan daftar harga "
"dapat dikonfigurasi untuk diterapkan pada template produk atau pada varian."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:287
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Inventory`: Inventory is counted for each individual product "
"variant. On the product template form, the inventory reflects the sum of all "
"variants, but the actual inventory is computed by individual variants."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Inventaris`: Inventaris dihitung untuk setiap varian produk "
"individual. Pada formulir template produk, inventaris mencerminkan jumlah "
"dari semua varian, tetapi inventaris aktual dihitung berdasarkan varian "
"individual."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:290
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Picture`: each product variant can have its own specific picture."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Picture`: setiap varian produk dapat memiliki gambar spesifiknya "
"sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:293
msgid ""
"Changes to the product template automatically apply to every variant of that "
"product."
msgstr ""
"Perubahan pada templat produk secara otomatis berlaku untuk setiap varian "
"produk tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:296
msgid ":doc:`import`"
msgstr ":doc:`import`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:3
msgid "Returns and refunds"
msgstr "Pengembalian dan pengembalian dana"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo *Sales* app provides two different ways to process returns. The "
"method used depends on whether or not an invoice has been sent."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi *Penjualan* Odoo menyediakan dua cara berbeda untuk memproses "
"pengembalian. Metode yang digunakan tergantung pada apakah faktur telah "
"dikirim atau belum."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:9
msgid "Before invoicing"
msgstr "Sebelum penagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:11
msgid ""
"Returns are completed using *Reverse Transfers* when a customer decides to "
"return a product **before** an invoice has been sent or validated."
msgstr ""
"Pengembalian diselesaikan menggunakan *Transfer Balik* ketika pelanggan "
"memutuskan untuk mengembalikan produk **sebelum** faktur dikirim atau "
"divalidasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:15
msgid ""
"In order to use *Reverse Transfers*, the *Inventory* app **must** be "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan *Transfer Balik*, aplikasi *Inventaris* **harus** diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:17
msgid ""
"To start a return before invoicing, navigate to the :menuselection:`Sales` "
"app, select the desired sales order, and click on the :guilabel:`Delivery` "
"smart button to open the associated delivery order."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memulai pengembalian sebelum penagihan, navigasikan ke aplikasi "
":menuselection:`Penjualan`, pilih sales order yang diinginkan, dan klik "
"tombol pintar :guilabel:`Pengiriman` untuk membuka surat jalan terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid ""
"A typical sales order with a highlighted delivery smart button in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Sales order pada umumnya dengan tombol pintar pengiriman yang disorot di "
"Odoo Penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:25
msgid "On the validated delivery order, click :guilabel:`Return`."
msgstr "Pada surat jalan yang telah divalidasi, klik :guilabel:`Pengembalian`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid ""
"A validated delivery order with a highlighted Return button in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Surat jalan yang telah divalidasi dengan tombol Pengembalian yang disorot di "
"Odoo Penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:31
msgid "This opens a :guilabel:`Reverse Transfer` pop-up window."
msgstr "Ini membuka jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Transfer Balik`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:33
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Quantity` matches the validated quantities from "
"the delivery order. Update the quantities, if necessary. Click on "
"the :guilabel:`🗑️ (trash)` icon next to a line item to remove it from the "
"return."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, :guilabel:`Kuantitas` sesuai dengan kuantitas yang telah "
"divalidasi dari surat jalan. Perbarui kuantitas jika diperlukan. Klik ikon "
":guilabel:`🗑️ (tempat sampah)` di sebelah item baris untuk menghapusnya dari "
"pengembalian."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid ""
"The \"Reverse Transfer\" pop-up window, to make a return before invoicing "
"the customer."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up \"Transfer Balik\", untuk melakukan pengembalian sebelum "
"menagih pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:41
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Return` to confirm the return. This generates a new "
"warehouse operation for the incoming returned product(s)."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Pengembalian` untuk mengonfirmasi pengembalian. "
"Ini menghasilkan operasi gudang baru untuk produk yang dikembalikan masuk."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid "Warehouse operation after a return has been confirmed in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Operasi gudang setelah pengembalian dikonfirmasi di Odoo Penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:48
msgid ""
"Upon receiving the return, the warehouse team validates the warehouse "
"operation by clicking :guilabel:`Validate`. Then, on the original sales "
"order, the :guilabel:`Delivered` quantity updates to reflect the difference "
"between the initial validated quantities and the returned quantities."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menerima pengembalian, tim gudang memvalidasi operasi gudang dengan "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Validasi`. Kemudian, pada sales order asli, kuantitas "
":guilabel:`Terkirim` diperbarui untuk mencerminkan selisih antara kuantitas "
"yang divalidasi awal dan kuantitas yang dikembalikan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid ""
"The updated \"Delivered\" quantity on the sales order after the reverse "
"transfer."
msgstr ""
"Kuantitas \"Terkirim\" yang diperbarui pada sales order setelah transfer "
"balik."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:56
msgid ""
"When an invoice is created, the customer receives an invoice **only** for "
"the products they are keeping, if any."
msgstr ""
"Ketika faktur dibuat, pelanggan menerima faktur **hanya** untuk produk yang "
"mereka simpan, jika ada."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:60
msgid "After invoicing"
msgstr "Setelah penagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:62
msgid ""
"Sometimes, customers return an item after they receive and/or pay for their "
"invoice. In these cases, a return using only *Reverse Transfers* is "
"insufficient since validated, or sent, invoices cannot be changed."
msgstr ""
"Terkadang, pelanggan mengembalikan barang setelah mereka menerima dan/atau "
"membayar faktur mereka. Dalam kasus ini, pengembalian menggunakan *Reverse "
"Transfers* saja tidak memadai karena faktur yang telah divalidasi atau "
"dikirim tidak dapat diubah."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:66
msgid ""
"However, *Reverse Transfers* can be used in conjunction with *Credit Notes* "
"to complete the customer's return."
msgstr ""
"Namun, *Reverse Transfers* dapat digunakan bersama dengan *Credit Notes* "
"untuk menyelesaikan pengembalian pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:69
msgid ""
"To start a return after invoicing, navigate to the relevant sales order in "
"the :menuselection:`Sales` app."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memulai pengembalian setelah penagihan, buka sales order yang relevan "
"di aplikasi :menuselection:`Penjualan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:72
msgid ""
"If there is a payment registered on the sales order, the payment details "
"appear in the chatter, and the invoice (accessible through "
"the :guilabel:`Invoices` smart button) has a green :guilabel:`In Payment` "
"banner."
msgstr ""
"Jika ada pembayaran yang terdaftar pada sales order, detail pembayaran "
"muncul di chatter, dan faktur (dapat diakses melalui tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`Invoices`) memiliki spanduk hijau :guilabel:`In Payment`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid "Sample of a green in payment banner in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Contoh spanduk hijau in payment di Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:80
msgid ""
"From the sales order, click on the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button to view "
"the validated delivery order. Then, click :guilabel:`Return` to open "
"the :guilabel:`Reverse Transfer` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Dari sales order, klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Delivery` untuk melihat "
"surat jalan yang telah divalidasi. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Return` untuk "
"membuka jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Reverse Transfer`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:83
msgid ""
"Next, edit the :guilabel:`Product` and/or :guilabel:`Quantity`, as needed "
"for the return. Then, click :guilabel:`Return`. This generates a new "
"warehouse operation for the incoming returned product(s), which is validated "
"by the warehouse team once the return is received by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Validate`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, edit :guilabel:`Product` dan/atau :guilabel:`Quantity` sesuai "
"kebutuhan untuk pengembalian. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Return`. Ini "
"menghasilkan operasi gudang baru untuk produk yang dikembalikan, yang "
"divalidasi oleh tim gudang setelah pengembalian diterima dengan mengklik "
":guilabel:`Validate`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:88
msgid ""
"Then, on the sales order, the :guilabel:`Delivered` quantity updates to "
"reflect the difference between the initial validated quantities and the "
"returned quantities."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, pada sales order, jumlah :guilabel:`Delivered` diperbarui untuk "
"mencerminkan perbedaan antara jumlah yang divalidasi awal dan jumlah yang "
"dikembalikan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:91
msgid ""
"To process a refund, navigate to the relevant invoice (from the sales order, "
"click on the :guilabel:`Invoices` smart button). Then, click "
"the :guilabel:`Credit Note` button at the top of the validated invoice."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memproses pengembalian dana, buka faktur yang relevan (dari sales "
"order, klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Invoices`). Kemudian, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Credit Note` di bagian atas faktur yang telah divalidasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid ""
"A typical customer invoice with a Credit Note button highlighted in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Faktur pelanggan biasa dengan tombol Credit Note yang disorot di Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:99
msgid "Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Credit Note` pop-up form."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan hal ini akan menampilkan formulir pop-up :guilabel:`Credit Note`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid "Typical credit note pop-up form that appears in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Formulir pop-up credit note biasa yang muncul di Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:105
msgid ""
"Start by entering a :guilabel:`Reason displayed on Credit Note` and a "
"specific :guilabel:`Journal` to process the credit. Then, select a "
"specific :guilabel:`Reversal Date`."
msgstr ""
"Mulai dengan memasukkan :guilabel:`Reason displayed on Credit Note` dan "
":guilabel:`Journal` tertentu untuk memproses kredit. Kemudian, pilih "
":guilabel:`Reversal Date` tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:108
msgid ""
"After the information is filled in, click :guilabel:`Reverse` "
"or :guilabel:`Reverse and Create Invoice`. Then, edit the draft, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Setelah informasi diisi, klik :guilabel:`Reverse` atau :guilabel:`Reverse "
"and Create Invoice`. Kemudian, edit draf jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:111
msgid "Lastly, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the credit note."
msgstr "Terakhir, klik :guilabel:`Confirm` untuk mengonfirmasi credit note."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:113
msgid ""
"When complete, a blue banner reading: :guilabel:`You have outstanding "
"credits for this customer. You can allocate them to mark this invoice as "
"paid.` appears at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"Setelah selesai, spanduk biru yang berbunyi :guilabel:`You have outstanding "
"credits for this customer. You can allocate them to mark this invoice as "
"paid.` muncul di bagian atas halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:117
msgid ":doc:`../../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:6
msgid "Sales quotations"
msgstr "Penawaran penjualan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:8
msgid ""
"A *sales quotation* or quote is a document sent to a customer that outlines "
"the estimated costs and terms for goods and services. Once accepted, a "
"quotation can be converted into a sales order, which serves as the final "
"agreement before delivery and invoicing."
msgstr ""
"*Penawaran penjualan* atau quote adalah dokumen yang dikirim kepada "
"pelanggan yang menguraikan perkiraan biaya dan ketentuan untuk barang dan "
"jasa. Setelah diterima, penawaran dapat dikonversi menjadi sales order, yang "
"berfungsi sebagai perjanjian akhir sebelum pengiriman dan penagihan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:13
msgid "Sales flow overview"
msgstr "Ikhtisar alur penjualan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:15
msgid ""
"Quotations fit into a broader sales flow that connects different stages of "
"customer interactions from initial interest to payment."
msgstr ""
"Penawaran harga cocok untuk alur penjualan yang lebih luas yang "
"menghubungkan berbagai tahap interaksi pelanggan dari minat awal hingga "
"pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:18
msgid "The typical flow follows these steps:"
msgstr "Alur umum mengikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:20
msgid ""
"*Quotation*: A proposal sent to the customer with product details and "
"pricing."
msgstr ""
"*Penawaran harga*: Proposal yang dikirim kepada pelanggan dengan detail "
"produk dan harga."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:21
msgid ""
"*Sales order*: Created automatically when the customer accepts the "
"quotation, confirming the sale."
msgstr ""
"*Sales order*: Dibuat secara otomatis ketika pelanggan menerima penawaran "
"harga, mengonfirmasi penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:23
msgid ""
"*Delivery* (if applicable): Products are shipped or services are delivered."
msgstr "*Pengiriman* (jika berlaku): Produk dikirim atau layanan diberikan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:24
msgid ""
"*Invoice*: The final bill is issued based on the sales order or delivered "
"products/services."
msgstr ""
"*Faktur*: Tagihan akhir diterbitkan berdasarkan sales order atau produk/"
"layanan yang dikirim."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:25
msgid ""
"*Payment*: The customer settles the invoice, completing the sales cycle."
msgstr ""
"*Pembayaran*: Pelanggan menyelesaikan faktur, melengkapi siklus penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:27
msgid ""
"This flow helps businesses track the entire lifecycle of a sale while "
"keeping information consistent across apps."
msgstr ""
"Alur ini membantu bisnis melacak seluruh siklus hidup penjualan sambil "
"menjaga informasi tetap konsisten di seluruh aplikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:30
msgid ""
"In Odoo, quotations are configured in the **Sales** app. They can also be "
"generated from other apps as part of the sales workflow:"
msgstr ""
"Di Odoo, penawaran harga dikonfigurasi dalam aplikasi **Penjualan**. "
"Penawaran harga juga dapat dibuat dari aplikasi lain sebagai bagian dari "
"alur kerja penjualan:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:33
msgid ""
"**CRM**: :doc:`Convert opportunities <../crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes>` "
"into quotes to follow up on potential deals."
msgstr ""
"**CRM**: :doc:`Ubah peluang <../crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes>` menjadi "
"penawaran harga untuk menindaklanjuti kesepakatan potensial."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Helpdesk**: :doc:`Generate quotes from tickets <../../services/helpdesk/"
"advanced/after_sales>` when offering paid services or products."
msgstr ""
"**Pusat Bantuan**: :doc:`Buat penawaran harga dari tiket <../../services/"
"helpdesk/advanced/after_sales>` ketika menawarkan layanan atau produk "
"berbayar."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:37
msgid ""
"**Subscriptions**: :doc:`Offer recurring services <../subscriptions>` before "
"starting an automatic billing cycle."
msgstr ""
"**Langganan**: :doc:`Tawarkan layanan berulang <../subscriptions>` sebelum "
"memulai siklus penagihan otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:42
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:3
msgid "Create quotations"
msgstr "Buat penawaran"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:42
msgid "Create, configure, and send quotations to customers."
