msgid ""
"`Convert the PDF into a PDF form <Adobe_>`_, then add a *dynamic form field* "
"at the location where the Odoo information should be inserted. Link the Odoo "
"fields to the *dynamic form fields* by double-clicking on the field to "
"open :guilabel:`Properties`."
msgstr ""
"`Konversi PDF menjadi formulir PDF <Adobe_>`_, lalu tambahkan *bidang "
"formulir dinamis* di lokasi di mana informasi Odoo harus disisipkan. "
"Hubungkan bidang Odoo ke *bidang formulir dinamis* dengan mengklik dua kali "
"pada bidang untuk membuka :guilabel:`Properties`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:71
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`General tab`, enter the name of the Odoo field for "
"the :guilabel:`Name`. Set the :guilabel:`Common Properties` "
"to :guilabel:`Visible` unless the field needs to be hidden until data is "
"populated."
msgstr ""
"Di :guilabel:`tab General`, masukkan nama bidang Odoo untuk "
":guilabel:`Name`. Atur :guilabel:`Common Properties` ke :guilabel:`Visible` "
"kecuali bidang perlu disembunyikan hingga data diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:75
msgid ""
"Next, click the :guilabel:`Appearance` tab and select the :guilabel:`Font "
"Size`, :guilabel:`Font Choice`, and :guilabel:`Text Color` to match the "
"template's existing text or branding. Click the :guilabel:`Options` tab and "
"set the text alignment to match the template’s design."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik tab :guilabel:`Appearance` dan pilih :guilabel:`Font "
"Size`, :guilabel:`Font Choice`, dan :guilabel:`Text Color` agar sesuai "
"dengan teks atau branding template yang ada. Klik tab :guilabel:`Options` "
"dan atur penjajaran teks agar sesuai dengan desain template."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:80
msgid "Generic PDF editor"
msgstr "Editor PDF generik"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:82
msgid ""
"Open the PDF with the PDF editor, add a *dynamic form field* where the Odoo "
"information is needed. Link the Odoo fields to the *dynamic form fields* by "
"opening the field’s :guilabel:`Properties` window. Then, in "
"the :guilabel:`Name` for that field, enter the name of the Odoo field."
msgstr ""
"Buka PDF dengan editor PDF, tambahkan *bidang formulir dinamis* di mana "
"informasi Odoo diperlukan. Hubungkan bidang Odoo ke *bidang formulir "
"dinamis* dengan membuka jendela :guilabel:`Properties` bidang. Kemudian, di "
":guilabel:`Name` untuk bidang tersebut, masukkan nama bidang Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:86
msgid ""
"If possible, configure the :guilabel:`Font Size`, :guilabel:`Font Choice`, "
"and :guilabel:`Text Color` to match the template's existing text or "
"branding. Click the :guilabel:`Options` tab and set the text alignment to "
"match the template’s design."
msgstr ""
"Jika memungkinkan, konfigurasikan :guilabel:`Font Size`, :guilabel:`Font "
"Choice`, dan :guilabel:`Text Color` agar sesuai dengan teks atau branding "
"template yang ada. Klik tab :guilabel:`Options` dan atur penjajaran teks "
"agar sesuai dengan desain template."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:93
msgid "Map PDF form fields to Odoo"
msgstr "Memetakan bidang formulir PDF ke Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:95
msgid ""
"This step connects any *dynamic form field* in the PDF to the corresponding "
"Odoo field by specifying the exact location of that information. Once the "
"PDF file is ready, save the changes and upload it to Odoo "
"via :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Headers/Footers` and "
"clicking :guilabel:`Upload`."
msgstr ""
"Langkah ini menghubungkan setiap *bidang formulir dinamis* di PDF ke bidang "
"Odoo yang sesuai dengan menentukan lokasi pasti dari informasi tersebut. "
"Setelah file PDF siap, simpan perubahan dan unggah ke Odoo melalui "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Penjualan --> Konfigurasi --> Header/Footer` dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Upload`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:100
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically detects *dynamic form fields* in the uploaded PDF and "
"displays the :guilabel:`Configure dynamic fields` link. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Configure dynamic fields` link to go to the :guilabel:`Form "
"Fields` page."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara otomatis mendeteksi *bidang formulir dinamis* di PDF yang "
"diunggah dan menampilkan tautan :guilabel:`Configure dynamic fields`. Klik "
"tautan :guilabel:`Configure dynamic fields` untuk membuka halaman "
":guilabel:`Form Fields`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:104
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Form Field Name` column is populated with the *dynamic form "
"fields* from the PDF. The :guilabel:`Path` column specifies the path to the "
"Odoo field corresponding to each *dynamic form field*."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Form Field Name` diisi dengan *bidang formulir dinamis* "
"dari PDF. Kolom :guilabel:`Path` menentukan jalur ke bidang Odoo yang sesuai "
"dengan setiap *bidang formulir dinamis*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:None
msgid "Configured text form fields in the PDF quote builder."
msgstr "Bidang formulir teks yang dikonfigurasi di pembuat penawaran PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:111
msgid ""
"To edit, click the :guilabel:`Path` cell of the desired form field row and "
"enter the Odoo field name. Refer to the :ref:`sales/pdf_quote_builder/"
"dynamic_text/common-dynamic-text-values` section for typical field names. "
"Refer to the :ref:`sales/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text/Odoo-field-path` "
"section for instructions on how to find Odoo field names and paths."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengedit, klik sel :guilabel:`Path` pada baris bidang formulir yang "
"diinginkan dan masukkan nama bidang Odoo. Lihat bagian :ref:`sales/"
"pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text/common-dynamic-text-values` untuk nama-nama "
"bidang umum. Lihat bagian :ref:`sales/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text/Odoo-"
"field-path` untuk instruksi tentang cara menemukan nama dan path bidang Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:119
msgid "Find Odoo field names or paths"
msgstr "Menemukan nama atau path bidang Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:121
msgid ""
"Users can enable :ref:`developer-mode` in Odoo and hover over the desired "
"field to see its technical name, which is the :guilabel:`Field` value in the "
"pop-up window. Or, while in Developer Mode, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Email Templates` menu. In the "
"search bar, search for \"Sales\", then open a *Sales template* to see "
"the :ref:`available dynamic form fields and their paths <email_template/"
"dynamic-placeholders>`."
msgstr ""
"Pengguna dapat mengaktifkan :ref:`developer-mode` di Odoo dan mengarahkan "
"kursor ke bidang yang diinginkan untuk melihat nama teknisnya, yaitu nilai "
":guilabel:`Field` di jendela pop-up. Atau, saat berada dalam Mode "
"Pengembang, navigasi ke menu :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> "
"Email Templates`. Di bilah pencarian, cari \"Sales\", lalu buka *template "
"Sales* untuk melihat :ref:`bidang formulir dinamis yang tersedia dan path-"
"nya <email_template/dynamic-placeholders>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:130
msgid "Configure custom dynamic form fields"
msgstr "Mengonfigurasi bidang formulir dinamis kustom"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:132
msgid ""
"To pull specific information from a sales order or a product that is not in "
"the :ref:`sales/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text/common-dynamic-text-values` "
"section, add a *dynamic form field* to the PDF with a unique name, then "
"configure the :guilabel:`Path` to point to the desired information in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menarik informasi spesifik dari sales order atau produk yang tidak ada "
"di bagian :ref:`sales/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text/common-dynamic-text-"
"values`, tambahkan *bidang formulir dinamis* ke PDF dengan nama unik, lalu "
"konfigurasikan :guilabel:`Path` untuk mengarah ke informasi yang diinginkan "
"di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:137
msgid ""
"When configuring the :guilabel:`Path`, use the dot (`.`) notation to specify "
"relationships between models. Headers and footers start from the "
"current :guilabel:`sale_order` model. Product documents follow their path "
"from :guilabel:`sale_order_line`."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengonfigurasi :guilabel:`Path`, gunakan notasi titik (`.`) untuk "
"menentukan hubungan antar model. Header dan footer dimulai dari model "
":guilabel:`sale_order` saat ini. Dokumen produk mengikuti path mereka dari "
":guilabel:`sale_order_line`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:142
msgid ""
"A company wants to display the customer's country in its quotations. To "
"display the customer's country in the quotation PDF, they used the dynamic "
"form field name :guilabel:`invoice_partner_country` in the PDF template. "
"After uploading the PDF to the **Sales** app, they set the :guilabel:`Path` "
"of the :guilabel:`Form Field Name` to:"
msgstr ""
"Sebuah perusahaan ingin menampilkan negara pelanggan dalam kuotasinya. Untuk "
"menampilkan negara pelanggan dalam PDF kuotasi, mereka menggunakan nama "
"bidang formulir dinamis :guilabel:`invoice_partner_country` dalam template "
"PDF. Setelah mengunggah PDF ke aplikasi **Penjualan**, mereka mengatur "
":guilabel:`Path` dari :guilabel:`Form Field Name` ke:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:147
msgid ""
"For a header or footer "
"document: :guilabel:`partner_invoice_id.country_id.name`"
msgstr ""
"Untuk dokumen header atau footer: "
":guilabel:`partner_invoice_id.country_id.name`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:0
msgid "The customer's country form field pathing for a quotation."
msgstr "Pathing bidang formulir negara pelanggan untuk kuotasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:152
msgid ""
"Example of Odoo's Form Field Path for the customer's country from a "
"quotation."
msgstr "Contoh Form Field Path Odoo untuk negara pelanggan dari kuotasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:154
msgid ""
"For a product "
"document: :guilabel:`order_id.partner_invoice_id.country_id.name`"
msgstr ""
"Untuk dokumen produk: :guilabel:`order_id.partner_invoice_id.country_id.name`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:0
msgid "The customer's country form field pathing from the product document."
msgstr "Pathing bidang formulir negara pelanggan dari dokumen produk."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:159
msgid ""
"Example of Odoo's Form Field Path for the customer's country from a product "
"document."
msgstr "Contoh Form Field Path Odoo untuk negara pelanggan dari dokumen produk."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:164
msgid "Create a custom note form field"
msgstr "Membuat bidang formulir catatan kustom"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:166
msgid ""
"When uploading any PDF containing the form field :guilabel:`custom_note`, "
"leaving the :guilabel:`Path` empty allows the seller to add any note to that "
"form field in the document, which shown when the PDF is built."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengunggah PDF apa pun yang berisi bidang formulir "
":guilabel:`custom_note`, membiarkan :guilabel:`Path` kosong memungkinkan "
"penjual untuk menambahkan catatan apa pun ke bidang formulir tersebut dalam "
"dokumen, yang ditampilkan saat PDF dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:173
msgid "Custom note field name with an empty Path cell."
msgstr "Nama bidang catatan kustom dengan sel Path kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:173
msgid ""
"Leave the :guilabel:`Path` column cell empty for the :guilabel:`custom_note` "
"row."
msgstr ""
"Biarkan sel kolom :guilabel:`Path` kosong untuk baris "
":guilabel:`custom_note`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:178
msgid "Quote Builder tab with note field to customize."
msgstr "Tab Quote Builder dengan bidang catatan untuk dikustomisasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:178
msgid ""
"The note field in the *Header* section in the :guilabel:`Quote Builder` tab "
"on a quotation."
msgstr ""
"Bidang catatan di bagian *Header* dalam tab :guilabel:`Quote Builder` pada "
"kuotasi."

